Description: We are currently working to update our laptops from Endpoint Protector 5.6.11 to 6.2.4.1003 using Intune as MDM, but in our pilot group of laptops, 2 of them are showing the exit code 1603, that means any conflicting app is interrupting the installation. We already deleted any registry keys of previous installations or attempts to install related to the appID or searching by titles containing "endpoint protector" but the issues is still happening.
